align=center><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 16.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: "微软雅黑",sans-serif; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: #1676c0'>问：什么是合同取得成本？</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 16.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: "微软雅黑",sans-serif; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; COLOR: #1676c0; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></H1>
<P class=MsoNormal 
